chart.caption: Referers
chart.sql: SELECT Count(Statv2Session.Statv2SessionID) AS CountOfStatv2SessionID, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionFirstpage, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionYear, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionMonth, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionRefererSearchWord FROM Statv2Session GROUP BY Statv2Session.Statv2SessionFirstpage, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionYear, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionMonth, Statv2Session.Statv2SessionRefererSearchWord HAVING ((Statv2Session.Statv2SessionFirstpage=965) AND (Statv2Session.Statv2SessionYear>=2006) AND (Statv2Session.Statv2SessionMonth>=1)) AND (Statv2Session.Statv2SessionRefererSearchWord='søgemaskineoptimering'OR Statv2Session.Statv2SessionRefererSearchWord='søgemaskiner')ORDER BY Statv2Session.Statv2SessionYear DESC , Statv2Session.Statv2SessionMonth DESC , Statv2Session.Statv2SessionRefererSearchWord
